        <div class="tab-content yanimda-anasayfa" id="flightSearchContent">
                <div class="tab-pane mb-5 fade   our-approach-tabs" id="our-approach" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="our-approach-tab">

                                        <div class="bg-lightgray">
                                            <div class="container">
                                                <div class="row ">
                                                    <div class="col-md-12  d-flex align-items-center">
                                                        <div class="mt-md-0 mt-5">
                                                                <div class="hizmet-title">
                                                                    <h3>OUR FOCUS IS THE WORLD, OUR GOAL IS THE FUTURE</h3>
                                                                </div>
                                                            <div class="alt-desc mb-4">
                                                                <p>At iGA Istanbul Airport, our aim is to <em><strong>"introduce the mobility methods of the future, using technology to benefit both humanity and the environment, while providing our guests with a comfortable and secure travel experience in the place where different cultures meet"</strong></em>.</p>

                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="container surdurulebilirlik">
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class="col-12">
                                                    <div class="alt-title">
                                                        <h3></h3>

                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="surdurSlider mt-5 negativeMargin" id="surdurSlider-0">
                                                            <div class="item">
                                                                <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/ybef5mya/artwist-413x464px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                <div class="slider-text">
                                                                    <h1>We Are Working Towards the Future of Mobility </h1>
                                                                    <p><p>Through the development of our innovative digital mobility practices, our guests, who come from all over the world, will be provided with a safe and inclusive travel experience, with our expertise allowing us to lead the way in aviation and mobility services.</p></p>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="item">
                                                                <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/xmnjcslh/standartlar.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                <div class="slider-text">
                                                                    <h1>We are Committed to Maintaining Environmental Integrity </h1>
                                                                    <p><p>Our focus is on eliminating the environmental footprint left by our aircraft and mobility services. In providing our services, we are implementing crucial operations to minimize the resources used and ensure cyclical waste management. Since the very start of our operations, we have dedicated specific projects aimed at preserving our biodiversity.</p></p>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="item">
                                                                <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/1ytda42k/carbon.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                <div class="slider-text">
                                                                    <h1>Adding Value to Our Society, Guests, and Employees </h1>
                                                                    <p><p>With a focus on regional development, we offer a range of employment opportunities in line with our commitment to responsible corporate citizenship. We invest in our society and in the communities that promote culture and art, to make a positive social impact. We employ a transparent and equitable management approach.</p></p>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="button-content mt-4" id="surdurSlider-button-0">
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="featured-slider-dots" id="surdurSlider-dots-0">
                                                        <span></span>
                                                    </div>
