                                        <div class="bg-gray">
                                            <div class="container">
                                                <div class="row ">
                                                    <div class="col-md-7  d-flex align-items-center">
                                                        <div class="mt-md-0 mt-5">
                                                                <div class="hizmet-title">
                                                                    <h3>Our Sustainability Reports</h3>
                                                                </div>
                                                            <div class="alt-desc mb-4">
                                                                <p>We are pleased to announce the publication of our 2020 Sustainability Report, showcasing our commitment to sustainability as an integral aspect of our corporate culture. This report highlights our environmental, social, and economic contributions in line with the Sustainable Development Goals.</p>

                                                            </div>
                                                                <div class="read-details black">
                                                                    <a href="/en/corporate/sustainability/?tab=2#gren-library">
                                                                        <span class="text">View Green Library</span>
                                                                        <span class="icon icon-chevron-right"></span>
                                                                    </a>
                                                                </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                        <div class="col-md-3 my-5 offset-md-2">
                                                            <div class="default-card">
                                                                <div class="card-content">
                                                                    <div class="content-body">
                                                                        <div class="main-title">
                                                                            <span>Our Sustainability Reports </span>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                        <div class="read-details black mt-5">
                                                                            <a href="/media/1lpj43gj/2021-22-sustainability-report-1.pdf" data-type="iframe" class="gallerypdf">
                                                                                <span class="text">View</span>
                                                                                <span class="icon icon-chevron-right"></span>
                                                                            </a>
                                                                        </div>

                                                                        <div class="download">
                                                                            <span class="">15.17 MB</span>
                                                                            <a href="/media/1lpj43gj/2021-22-sustainability-report-1.pdf" target="_blank">
                                                                                <span class="icon icon-download"></span>
                                                                            </a>
                                                                        </div>

                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="card-img">
                                                                    <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/nocl1waj/artboard-2-100-300x282.jpg?format=webp" alt="">
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="container surdurulebilirlik mt-2">
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class="col-12">
                                                    <div class="alt-title">
                                                        <h1>Our Environmental Strategy</h1>

                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="cevreselGrid">

                                                        <div class="row mb-5">
                                                                <div class="col-md-4 small mt-5">
                                                                    <div class="item">
                                                                        <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/0sulngrh/iklim-degisikligi520x520px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                        <div class="text">
                                                                            <div class="alt-title">
                                                                                <h1>Adapting to Climate Change: Achieving Carbon Neutrality by 2050 </h1>
                                                                                <p>Our carbon management activities are conducted according to the procedures prepared in line with the Standard 14064-1 Quantification and Reporting of Greenhouse Gas Emissions and Removals at the Organizational Level.</p>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="col-md-8 big mt-5">
                                                                    <div class="item">
                                                                        <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/qu4j4hj0/enerji-verimliligi880x520px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                        <div class="text">
                                                                            <div class="alt-title">
                                                                                <h1>Energy Efficiency</h1>
                                                                                <p>In accordance with our Energy Management Policy, the ISO 50001 Energy Management System has been installed and we are implementing effective practices to promote conscious consumption and energy savings. In addition to implementing system-based energy efficiency practices, we monitor the consumption of all our systems for any unusual activity and take the appropriate measures when necessary.</p>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="col-md-8 big mt-5">
                                                                    <div class="item">
                                                                        <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/ww3d5rbp/kati-atik-yonetimi880x520px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                        <div class="text">
                                                                            <div class="alt-title">
                                                                                <h1>Zero Waste</h1>
                                                                                <p>Our waste management system has been implemented throughout our business and has been designed in line with our 'Zero Waste' objective, fostering a shared approach among all our stakeholders. Within this context, our priority is to minimize waste, a process that we facilitate through our sophisticated waste management system, using separation at source and quadruple separation containers. Our recycling practices use the semi-automated separation system that has been established at Istanbul Airport.</p>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="col-md-4 small mt-5">
                                                                    <div class="item">
                                                                        <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/p1cj2afd/su-ve-atik-su-yonetimi520x520px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                        <div class="text">
                                                                            <div class="alt-title">
                                                                                <h1>Water and Wastewater Management </h1>
                                                                                <p>We recognize the importance of water as a vital and scarce resource. With this awareness, we conduct ISO 14046 Water Footprint Standard studies throughout iGA Istanbul Airport, with the aim of understanding and evaluating the extent and significance of the potential environmental impacts caused by our activities. We anticipate that the inability to feed water sources will become an increasingly crucial challenge due to increased consumption and pollution, and that the Water Footprint Standard will evolve into the Zero Water Footprint concept in the near future.</p>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="col-md-12 big mt-5">
                                                                    <div class="item">
                                                                        <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/fwvnrjaa/biyocesitlilik-1440x520px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                        <div class="text">
                                                                            <div class="alt-title">
                                                                                <h1>Biodiversity and Wildlife Management </h1>
                                                                                <p>We at iGA Istanbul Airport strive to reduce the impact of our operations on natural ecosystems and biodiversity and intend to eliminate these impacts using supplementary measures. Our efforts to preserve biological assets at iGA Istanbul Airport continue, following the Biodiversity Action Plan (BAP), which we implemented in 2015.</p>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                        </div>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="container surdurulebilirlik mt-2">
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class="col-12">
                                                    <div class="alt-title">
                                                        <h1>Our Social Approach</h1>

                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="cevreselGrid">

                                                        <div class="row mb-5">
                                                                <div class="col-md-8 big mt-5">
                                                                    <div class="item">
                                                                        <img src="https://www.istairport.com/media/dnaputtw/sosyal-sorumluluk-projeleri880x520px.jpg?format=webp" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                                        <div class="text">
                                                                            <div class="alt-title">
                                                                                <h1>Our Social Responsibility and Community Benefit Projects </h1>
                                                                                <p>As an integral part of our unwavering commitment to sustainability, we strive to deliver significant benefits to underprivileged communities through our Social Investment Program, encompassing a range of fast-impact and sustainable development initiatives.</p>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
